        "action": "Require council tax reductions for those affected by antisocial behaviour ",
        "additional_details": "I believe this will help hold councils accountable.",
        "background": "I want the Government to require that local authorities reduce council tax for residents affected by antisocial behaviour of neighbours who live in council housing. This could be done by introducing a points system that monitors and assesses each episode of antisocial behaviour.",
